# **LLMWorkbook**

[![CodeQL Advanced](https://github.com/aryadhruv/LLMWorkbook/actions/workflows/codeql.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/aryadhruv/LLMWorkbook/actions/workflows/codeql.yml)
